; ─── Recommendation ────────────────────────────────────────────

(recommendation
  :short "Wait for blocker 1 (worktree stability) before landing JS impls. Land schema-status slices for the 10 real verbs as low-risk incremental progress."
  :long "The concurrent multi-lane push is not architecturally safe as-configured. Each lane should be in its own worktree, or the coordinator should serialize per-lane merges through a broker. Without that isolation, no lane can honestly claim REPL-verified per-verb commits — the CLI's health depends on the union of every lane's uncommitted state at that instant."
)
